**Rules for adding new files:**
- New AI prompt? → `lib/ai/prompts/{name}.ts`, exported as a function returning `{ system, user }` or `Content[]`.
- New DB query? → If reused, put in `lib/db/queries/{entity}.ts`. One-off queries can stay in Server Actions.
