## 11. Self-hosting compatibility

Every change must work for someone running `docker compose up` on a fresh VPS.

**Checklist before merging:**
- [ ] `.env.example` updated if new env vars
- [ ] `docker-compose.yml` updated if new services
- [ ] `Dockerfile` builds clean
- [ ] No hardcoded paths outside `STORAGE_PATH`
- [ ] No localhost-only assumptions (use `process.env.PORT`, etc.)
- [ ] No external service dependencies (Sentry, S3, etc.) required for happy path
- [ ] README updated if new setup step

